title: #92Noon Live from TCO: Boudreau / Wobby / Abdullah
description:
The FAN's Bruce Boudreau joins PA and Nordo in the first segment to recap last night's loss to the Toronto Maple Leafs.

Then, it's hardcore football the rest of the way: 92Noon tunes into Mike Zimmer's Wednesday Press Conference, and welcomes Vikings RB Ameer Abdullah into the show in the final hour.
